{"tid":2361442,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"被國安拘捕　印裔社工安德里：仍深愛香港　繼續熱衷分享少數族裔文化","createTime":"2021-01-10T15:51:39.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-10T15:58:08.000Z","uid":212249,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"3b15c0938ed818d01b1a55b86964d7a118ac4767","tid":2361442,"uid":212249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-10T15:51:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/20200110-05_aNv84_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2F20200110-05_aNv84_1200x0.png&h=09bb6356&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n警方上周以《國安法》，拘捕 55 名參與去年民主派的人，包括融樂會副主席、印裔社工安德里（Jeffrey Andrews）。他獲保釋後今（10日）在FB發文稱，感謝親朋支持，並自言事後仍深愛香港，亦會繼續熱衷於社工的工作，以及分享少數族裔的多元文化（beautiful diversity）。<br />\n<br />\n安德里憶述，他當天被警察鎖上手扣時，妻子在一旁就如戰士般（warrior），沒流眼淚。他及後致電父親時，想起20年前他曾因犯事被捕，今次被捕卻是出於政治理念。安德里起初還擔心父親得悉後會恐慌（panic attack），甚至中風，但父親卻安慰他：「不用擔心，你會沒事的；我會為你祈禱。」安德利形容，其父親如漫威英雄鐵甲奇俠（Iron Man），其妻子則如女超人（Super Woman)。<br />\n<br />\n安德里又說，他起初以為身邊人得悉此事後會疏遠自己，並與其家人保持距離。但讓他驚訝的是，還有無數人在支持自己。他最後重申，事後仍熱愛香港，因為這城為他自己、其家人及社區帶來很多美好。"},{"pid":"522edff8178942908bcbe803b0ac1d2dbd8510f7","tid":2361442,"uid":212249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-10T15:52:18.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/112620733826853/posts/213760503712875/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F112620733826853%2Fposts%2F213760503712875%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=7oH93WZedTbABA3XB48d7RZhTFX1FVJLw6RhI%2FCRHR8%3D&h=bc99ca0a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/112620733826853/posts/213760503712875/?d=n</a><br />\n上去比個like+留言支持下佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/gun.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"765c77035438ae3875c1bd480b0628add54fab07","tid":2361442,"uid":364770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-10T15:52:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35a65c0a08435a2fbaaaaac32f6bebf93b1baf2d","tid":2361442,"uid":51820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-10T15:53:03.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"98c86152df06eb85f9e72da3bc3ed90f2ebc16d4","tid":2361442,"uid":212249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-10T15:54:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e301ce2740976393120c61ca1ebb0548b0d18ee7","tid":2361442,"uid":212249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-10T15:55:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/gun.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cef61e8a795f73eb258999489ce07df89ffddb89","tid":2361442,"uid":235152,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-10T15:58:08.000Z","msg":"佢應該好難告得入<br />\n係選舉論譠入面佢解答重温和過泛民<br />\n本土派部份民主派入硬<br />\n但政治上參加唔到選舉"}]}